sources.title: The Boob Tube 1975
sources.description: Classic Drive-in fare from the 70's. Sadly this is the best copy that I can find. They all seem to be based on a single damaged AVI file. Did a bit of work to clean this up but there is not much to be done with a file that encoded badly from the start. Still, great fun, silly movie, and Colleen Brennan.
